metadata.description:
RANDOMLY ACCESSED MEMORIES 01 //

DYSPATHIC MAGNETISM X CONTRAVENTIONAL LANDSCAPES

This series of work considers the incidental moments that form subliminal memories, simultaneously intentionally questioning traditional rationale around photographic expression.
